  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>... that the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Wedding\" title=\"Red Wedding\">Red Wedding</a> is inspired by two similar events in Scottish history, the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clan_Douglas\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Clan Douglas\">Black Dinner</a> and the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Massacre_of_Glencoe\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Massacre of Glencoe\">Glencoe Massacre</a>?<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rssm1170.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rssm1170.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Did_you_know/53&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><span class=\"citation news\">Hibberd,&#32;James&#32;(June 2, 2013).&#32;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://insidetv.ew.com/2013/06/02/game-of-thrones-author-george-r-r-martin-why-he-wrote-the-red-wedding/2/\">\"'Game of Thrones' author George R.R. Martin: Why he wrote the Red Wedding\"</a>.&#32;<i>Entertainmaint Weekly</i><span class=\"printonly\">.&#32;<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://insidetv.ew.com/2013/06/02/game-of-thrones-author-george-r-r-martin-why-he-wrote-the-red-wedding/2/\">http://insidetv.ew.com/2013/06/02/game-of-thrones-author-george-r-r-martin-why-he-wrote-the-red-wedding/2/</a></sp